caption: It's all in the details at La Social. Everything from their vibrant decor, pastel dishes, gold flatware and gorgeously prepared salads really highlights their attention to detail.  I really enjoyed the carrot & ginger soup, which was plated …

I went to La Social today good quality healthy sandwiches, its a clean neat restaurant much much better than others around that area I was with 2 other people and we all like the sandwiches, I recomend this restaurant.
